title: "Obsessive Fishing Disorder" font ID request.
content:
First off, thanks so much for taking a look.

I've been looking for days and can't seem to locate it. I'm at my wits end!

Does anyone recognize the font used here for "Obsessive Fishing Disorder"?

Thanks in advance!

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415183443im_/http:/typophile.com/files/front_5282.jpg)
author: Gabewhite

comments.content: It's **[Mischievous](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415183443/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Dafont-5%20%2F%20%28Freemium%29&ffam=Mischievous%20-%20Regular&fid=aaabc9b2231881447c21f71e91bc6813&fsize=60&text=Obsessive%20Fishing%20Disorder&wrap=2)** free font by Alexander Mann

You're a life saver and a genius. I don't know who you are, but you're a gentleman and a scholar.

Thank you.
